entries.journal_entry_description: Qakkee believes he's the greatest hunter in the galaxy. Prove that you are his equal!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The final challenge from Qakkee is to hunt down one of the Rancors on Dathomir and bring back one of its teeth.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have done it! Return to Qakkee with the Rancor tooth.
